The [[Gados]] species from [[Abregado-rae/Legends|Abregado-rae]] spoke a '''native language''' early in their history. This was an ancient language, but it slowly faded from use when the Gados opened their world to settlers from other planets. The Gados culture slowly eroded similarly.<ref name="CatCW" />

